    </tablecell>
    <tablecell>
      <paragraph role="paragraph" id="par_id3158444" xml-lang="en-US"><ahelp hid=".uno:Edit">Creates a text box.</ahelp> Text boxes are fields in which the user can enter text. In a form, text boxes display data or allow for new data input.</paragraph>
